{"TopicId":210034,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Is there a mod for suit witch in flight?","CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-08T15:07:11Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-08T15:07:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need a mod so my astronauts can change suits in flight. I want to have my astronauts go from the ACES to the EMU.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-08T15:35:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224183269\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221665241631\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need a mod so my astronauts can change suits in flight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou need a mod that is still work in progress. but it does the job.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstall Sunkworks by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106975\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Angel-125\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Download from the GitHub link.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4376264618\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/202746-min-ksp-111-wip-sunkworks-maritime-technologies/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt has wonderful parts for doing things underwater, but you won\u0027t need them for your purpose. What you do need is to make an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E patch to add the\u00A0WBISuitSwitcher to all crewed parts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E// adds suit changer to all parts with IVA\n// modified by: Caerfinon Original by: ColdJ\n\n@PART[*]:HAS[@INTERNAL[*]:HAS[!MODULE[WBISuitSwitcher]]]:FINAL\n{\n    MODULE\n    {\n        name = WBISuitSwitcher\n    }\n} \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen just right click the crew part in flight and select Change Wardrobe\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jBe5LONl.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002288.13\u0022 height=\u0022564\u0022 width=\u0022640\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/jBe5LONl.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen you can pick any suit from the stock suit picker to wear...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00224bmLXcNl.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002255.00\u0022 height=\u0022352\u0022 width=\u0022640\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/4bmLXcNl.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBe the best dressed Kerbal anywhere.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-10-08T15:36:11Z\u0022 title=\u002210/08/2022 03:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 8, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Caerfinon\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}